title: [P3D] PMDG 737 NGX (SP1D)
description:
Hi Guys, found this one just lying around on the net. Didn't found one here (or i'm 

blind)

Before you start asking any questions:

- Yes it's 100% working (tried myself)

- It's only for P3D (working gr8 in 2.5 with hotfixes)

- To Weather Radar to work properly you need Active Sky Next for your weather engine 

- No viruses (at least AVG didn't found any )

- It's working with FS2Crew Emergency 2.3 (to install FS2Crew in P3D you need Estonia 

Migration Tool)


If you find any errors feel free to RAGE ;)


If you Like the software please consider buying it !
